  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>转生魔塔</strong>是一个集合了roguelike/塔防等等元素的竖向割草游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为勇者的玩家在转生成为魔塔之后，利用陷阱与魔塔能力，打败魔物以及魔王。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >切割敌人</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292410/extras/61d8e53f78920a210561a046636885bb.poster.avif?t=1761533661\" width=500 height=500 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292410/extras/61d8e53f78920a210561a046636885bb.webm?t=1761533661\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292410/extras/61d8e53f78920a210561a046636885bb.mp4?t=1761533661\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >和切水果一样，来切割所有敌人！割草游戏，没点切割感，能叫割草吗？</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >庞大的技能组</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292410/extras/b5145be819800f6c4839375348c75a24.avif?t=1761533661\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292410/extras_big/b5145be819800f6c4839375348c75a24.avif?t=1761533661 width=800 height=512 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多种流派，100+个技能供你决定魔塔的成长路线</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >两种不同技能还有可能组合成更强大的组合技能，助你抵御敌人的进攻波次。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏机制·三消</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292410/extras/987d014c9b4ab98a9eb84b5977761ed6.poster.avif?t=1761533661\" width=500 height=500 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292410/extras/987d014c9b4ab98a9eb84b5977761ed6.webm?t=1761533661\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292410/extras/987d014c9b4ab98a9eb84b5977761ed6.mp4?t=1761533661\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >任意三个相同的敌人/同类型的物品连续时，可以触发三消。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >三消的敌人将会被直接击败，三消的物品将会提前获得</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >同时：三消还可以触发三消技能组的效果，三消或许会成为通关的秘诀之一</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >多种游戏模式</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >除了基础的模式之外，游戏内还有其他模式供玩家挑战</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>时停模式</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >除非MP用尽以及敌人行动之后，时间将不会流逝</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >只有长按[或者按主空格键]时，时间会流逝</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >特殊技能将被禁止获取及使用</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >敌人类别更加集中；只可以通过点击攻击敌人，无法切割敌人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>对决模式</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >敌人将不主动攻击，受到普通攻击时，无视距离进行反击;敌人攻击成长减为1/10</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >魔塔通过点击来攻击敌人，无法切割敌人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >地图有空位时，就会一直生成事件。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个事件消失（如敌人死亡、物品被获得）时，时间会流逝</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>转生魔塔</strong>是一个集合了roguelike/塔防等等元素的竖向割草游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为勇者的玩家在转生成为魔塔之后，利用陷阱与魔塔能力，打败魔物以及魔王。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >切割敌人</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292410/extras/61d8e53f78920a210561a046636885bb.poster.avif?t=1761533661\" width=500 height=500 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292410/extras/61d8e53f78920a210561a046636885bb.webm?t=1761533661\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292410/extras/61d8e53f78920a210561a046636885bb.mp4?t=1761533661\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >和切水果一样，来切割所有敌人！割草游戏，没点切割感，能叫割草吗？</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >庞大的技能组</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292410/extras/b5145be819800f6c4839375348c75a24.avif?t=1761533661\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292410/extras_big/b5145be819800f6c4839375348c75a24.avif?t=1761533661 width=800 height=512 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多种流派，100+个技能供你决定魔塔的成长路线</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >两种不同技能还有可能组合成更强大的组合技能，助你抵御敌人的进攻波次。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏机制·三消</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292410/extras/987d014c9b4ab98a9eb84b5977761ed6.poster.avif?t=1761533661\" width=500 height=500 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292410/extras/987d014c9b4ab98a9eb84b5977761ed6.webm?t=1761533661\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292410/extras/987d014c9b4ab98a9eb84b5977761ed6.mp4?t=1761533661\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >任意三个相同的敌人/同类型的物品连续时，可以触发三消。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >三消的敌人将会被直接击败，三消的物品将会提前获得</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >同时：三消还可以触发三消技能组的效果，三消或许会成为通关的秘诀之一</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >多种游戏模式</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >除了基础的模式之外，游戏内还有其他模式供玩家挑战</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>时停模式</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >除非MP用尽以及敌人行动之后，时间将不会流逝</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >只有长按[或者按主空格键]时，时间会流逝</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >特殊技能将被禁止获取及使用</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >敌人类别更加集中；只可以通过点击攻击敌人，无法切割敌人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>对决模式</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >敌人将不主动攻击，受到普通攻击时，无视距离进行反击;敌人攻击成长减为1/10</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >魔塔通过点击来攻击敌人，无法切割敌人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >地图有空位时，就会一直生成事件。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个事件消失（如敌人死亡、物品被获得）时，时间会流逝</p>",
